%e A387001 The number of vertices is a(5) = 17.
%e A387001 The number of faces is A000203(5) = 6.
%e A387001 The number of edges is 2*A155085(5) = 2*11 = 22.
%e A387001 The number of edges with the same orientation is A155085(5) = 11.
